Summary: An Argentine anarcho-syndicalist newspaper, published in Buenos Aires by labor activists beginning in 1905. Issues in this collection include: 1, no.11 (11 ene 1905) - no.12 (21 ene 1905); no.17 (16 abr 1906); 2, no.22 (1 jul 1906) - no.38 (1 mar 1907); no.42 (1 may 1907) - no.43 (16 may 1907); 5, no.111 (12 feb 1910) - no.112 (19 feb 1910); no.118 (18 abr 1910); no.128 (30 ago 1910).
